                        <p class="text-[var(--mks-bone)]/80 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-sm font-light">A contemporary dialogue between structural Southern African knitwear matrices and razor-sharp modern tailoring.</p>
                        <button onclick="app.router.navigate('shop')" class="px-10 py-5 btn-mks-dark text-xs">
                            View Lookbook Edit
                        </button>
                    </div>
