                <span class="font-display text-2xl tracking-tighter block text-[var(--mks-bone)]">M A K H E S A</span>
                <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-sm">An architectural fashion system preserving southern structural lineages through premium, sustainable textile expressions. Handcrafted iteratively.</p>
            </div>
